gin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #2f3235;\"> displacementFilter.</span><span class=\"enlighter-m3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #0086b3;\">scale</span><span class=\"enlighter-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #2f3235;\">.</span><span class=\"enlighter-m3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #0086b3;\">x</span><span class=\"enlighter-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #2f3235;\"> = </span><span class=\"enlighter-g1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #777777;\">(</span><span class=\"enlighter-k9\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #990073; font-weight: bold;\">window</span><span class=\"enlighter-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #2f3235;\">.</span><span class=\"enlighter-m3\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #0086b3;\">innerWidth</span><span class=\"enlighter-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #2f3235;\"> </span><span class=\"enlighter-e2\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: inherit; font-size: 13px; font-family: inherit; color: #009926;\">/ 2 - e.clientX) /20</span><span class=\"enlighter-text\" style=\"box-sizing: bor